name: A Tale of Frequency
description:
As the SheWarriors came together, putting their differences aside to defend their Queens, they found beauty.
They found a similar distaste for corruption.
This temporary coherence between them was a necessary yet unfamiliar union for many.
Yet it was questioned by none.
The truth is the truth of which all accept.

🔥 24 Hour Burn Notice 🔥 Each SheWarrior collector will receive an airdrop soon.
